<div class="a-desc">
  <p>Care4Nation stands in solidarity with the COVID-19 warriors and has been lending support to frontline workers and medical and paramedical staff with PPE kits, hygiene kits and hospital infrastructure supplementation. We have distributed 39,000+ PPE kits to ASHA, ANM and Anganwadi workers and 12,000+ hospital staff. 16,000+ frontline workers have also been supported with hygiene kits. Additionally, 300,000 triple layer masks and 100,000 gloves have been distributed.</p>
